    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><strong>Hild</strong> is a Dwarf innkeeper who runs the Broken Stair Inn — the only inn in Stairwatch. She asks no questions, charges fair prices, and waters the ale 'just enough to be annoying.' She knows Lew well — he owes her three nights' lodging.</p><p>Hild is practical, no-nonsense, and generous when earned. She is the warm heart of Stairwatch: practical kindness in a world that's running out of it.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
